 labour is in the concurrent list  two ceilings are provided  under  the  act  namely  eligibility  limit  which  is  rs  10000  per  month and the calculation ceiling rs 3500  in this bill the eligibility limit is proposed to  be  increased  from  rs  10000  per  month  to  rs  21000  per  month    the calculation  ceiling  is  also  be  raised  from  rs  3500  to  rs  7000  or  the  minimum wage for the scheduled employment  hon prime minister desired that this benefit be  made  effective  from  the  1st  day  of  april  2014  for  which  an  official amendment  would  be  moved    i  am  also  thankful  to  the  hon  prime  minister  for giving this advance new year gift to crores of poor workers of our country    